/target
**/*.rs.bk
*.pdb
.DS_Store

# Author-private notes: rich CLAUDE.md context, internal worked-example
# paper slices that cite unpublished code, design history. Not shipped.
/internal-notes/

# .claude/ is excluded by some global gitignores; the agents and slash commands
# in this repo ARE part of the project and must be tracked. Negate the ignore
# for the parts we own; keep settings.local.json (per-user) excluded.
!.claude/
!.claude/agents/
!.claude/agents/**
!.claude/commands/
!.claude/commands/**
.claude/settings.local.json

# Codex skills are project-owned equivalents of the Claude agents/commands.
!.codex/
!.codex/prompts/
!.codex/prompts/**
!.codex/skills/
!.codex/skills/**
